			The operating company of YouTube is YouTube, LLC, 901  Cherry Ave., San Bruno, CA 94066, USA. YouTube, LLC is a subsidiary of Google  Inc., 1600 Amphitheatre Pkwy, Mountain View, CA 94043-1351, USA. <br>
